<body><page page_number="1" transcanno_page_id="2109"><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1534270709839"><div>Der <tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1534269187994" tran_correction_original="Zu*">Zug</tran_word_correction_id25></div></paragraph><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1534270709841"><div>Im Jahr 1944 wurden <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534268699728" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">viele</tran_word_deletion_id8> Juden im KZ</div><div>gebracht. Die Familie Schnitzelberg wurde <tran_hyphen_id15 class="medium-tran_hyphen_id15" tagcode="1534269731855" tran_hyphen_target="_#_">ent-</tran_hyphen_id15></div><div>deckt und mussten im KZ. Sie waren</div><div>Juden, doch der Vater entschied die</div><div>die Familie zu verstecken und <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534268706986" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">für</tran_word_deletion_id8> <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534268711464" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">sich</tran_word_deletion_id8></div><div>der Vater entschied für ihnen zu gehen.</div><div>Die Eltern wussten genau was ein KZ</div><div>war. Am 27. Jänner 1944 wurde der</div><div>Vater nach Auschwitz gebracht.</div><div>Er versteckt <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534269058326" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">i</tran_word_deletion_id8> seine Familie. Er</div><div>grüßte <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534269065881" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">das</tran_word_deletion_id8> <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534269069228" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">M</tran_word_deletion_id8> die Tochter gab ihr</div><div>eine Taube aus Ton. Das Mädchen</div><div><tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534269074763" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">frä</tran_word_deletion_id8> freute sich und umarmte ihn</div><div>fest wie sie konnte. <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534269079019" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">und</tran_word_deletion_id8> <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534269088605" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_"><tran_ambiguous_id3 class="medium-tran_ambiguous_id3" tagcode="1534269762050" tran_alternative_1="guchte" tran_alternative_2="">guckte</tran_ambiguous_id3></tran_word_deletion_id8></div><div>sie sagte dem Vater: "Danke Papi, wir</div><div>werden auf dir warten und werden</div><div>danach mein <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Geburtstag" tagcode="1534269773843">Gebutstag</orth_error_id12> feiern." Der</div><div>Vater lächelt sie an. Die Mutter</div><div>weinte und die Tochter verstand</div><div>es nicht warum sie weinte. Der</div></paragraph></page><page page_number="2" transcanno_page_id="2110"><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1534270709843"><div>Vater weinte <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534270518542" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">mit</tran_word_deletion_id8> auch umarmte sie</div><div>und gab ein Kuss auf der Wange</div><div>Er sagte: "Passt auf euch auf!"</div><div>Er stieg auf dem Zug schmiss den</div><div>Koffer auf dem Boden und gab</div><div><tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1534270602345" tran_correction_original="die*">die</tran_word_correction_id25> Hand <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534270532626" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">der</tran_word_deletion_id8> der <tran_unreadable_id17 class="medium-tran_unreadable_id17" tagcode="1534270538531"><tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534270649869" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">*</tran_word_deletion_id8></tran_unreadable_id17> Familie.</div><div>Der Zug starten und ließ sie</div><div>aus. Der Himmel war grau</div><div>wie der <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534270551146" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">B</tran_word_deletion_id8> Rauch. Es gaben</div><div>Löcher <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="verursacht" tagcode="1534270700499">veruhrsach</orth_error_id12> von <tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1534270622273" tran_correction_original="d*">den</tran_word_correction_id25></div><div>Bomben<tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534270561795" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">,</tran_word_deletion_id8> und keine <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Bäume" tagcode="1534270709838">Baume</orth_error_id12>. Die</div><div>Luft war schmutzig und die</div><div>Leute husteten. Die Familie stand</div><div>dort und wartete bis wenn</div><div>der Zug nicht verschwand.</div><div>Nach <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1534270573602" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">einig</tran_word_deletion_id8> ca. 20 Minuten</div><div>verschwand der Zug. Ab diesem</div><div>Moment kam der Vater nie</div><div>mehr zurück und die</div><div>Familie sah ihn nicht mehr</div></paragraph></page></body>
